doc.previous: Following the arrival of John Borghetti former Qantas senior executive as the CEO of Virgin Blue there was much speculation regarding a forthcoming rebrand of the airline 27
doc.after: A number of key Qantas staff moved to Virgin Blue while key Virgin Blue staff departed the airline 28 The airline further announced its intention to operate Airbus A330 aircraft between Perth and the East Coast starting in May 2011 29
